This dataset contain the images of actors of Tv show "The Big Bang Theory" [Howard, Leonard, Raj and Sheldon]. The data is downloaded from google images. The -Google Search directories contain the Raw Data, all renamed to respective actor names in directory.
I have cleaned the raw dataset using python script and "Cleaned Dataset" contains the cleaned data. I used opencv library to clean data, the images which has clear image and two eyes showing are selected and rest are rejected by the script.
title: The Big Bang Theory Actors
subtitle: Image Classification
description:
This dataset contain the images of actors of Tv show "The Big Bang Theory" [Howard, Leonard, Raj and Sheldon]. The data is downloaded from google images. The -Google Search directories contain the Raw Data, all renamed to respective actor names in directory.
I have cleaned the raw dataset using python script and "Cleaned Dataset" contains the cleaned data. I used opencv library to clean data, the images which has clear image and two eyes showing are selected and rest are rejected by the script.
